<item>
            <title>[SPR-10047] Add HandlerMethod as possible parameter to @ExceptionHandler method</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-10047</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the @ExceptionHandler method can not contain HandlerMethod as method parameter as it is not passed by spring framework.&lt;br/&gt;
It could be very helpful for investigating throwing exception method, for example, for custom annotations.&lt;br/&gt;
The workaround that I found is to create mvc interceptor and pass the MethodHandler via ServletRequest.attributtes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
